Description: The LCA110 is a normally open (1-Form-A) Solid State Relay which uses optically coupled MOSFET technology to provide 3750Vrms of input to output isolation. Its optically coupled outputs, which use the patented OptoMOS architecture, are controlled by a highly efficient GaAIAs infrared LED. The LCA110 can be used to replace mechanical relays, and offers the superior reliability associated with semiconductor devices.
